text.value: What is the weather in Centralia, PA?

The current weather in Centralia, PA is overcast with a temperature of 80°F (27°C). It feels like 82°F (28°C). The humidity is 42%, and the wind is blowing from the SSE at 2 mph (4 km/h). The atmospheric pressure is 1023 mb. Visibility is 9 miles (16 km). 

The forecast for the rest of the day indicates it will stay mostly sunny and clear, with temperatures reaching a high of 83°F (28°C) and a low of 56°F (14°C).
